OL,3,C'Absolutely amazing': Nursery reopens
OL,4,Cjust six weeks after major fire
OL,6,FThe owner of a nursery in Berkshire
OL,7,Fhas said it's "absolutely amazing"
OL,8,Fthat the site has reopened to children
OL,9,Fjust six weeks after it was destroyed
OL,10,Fby a major fire.
OL,12,FTigers Day Nursery in Thatcham burnt
OL,13,Fto the ground after it was engulfed by
OL,14,Ffire on 10 March 2026, with the cause
OL,15,Fnot yet known.
OL,17,FChildren who attended the nursery,
OL,18,Fwhich has been running for 30 years,
OL,19,Fhad to temporarily move to a site ten
OL,20,Fmiles away while the Thatcham site was
OL,21,Frebuilt.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
