OL,3,C'Absolutely amazing': Nursery reopens
OL,4,Cjust six weeks after major fire
OL,6,FNursery director Alison Huntley said
OL,7,Fthat the scale of the fire meant the
OL,8,Fimpact on the nursery was huge.
OL,10,FShe said: "Everything (needed
OL,11,Freplacing), toys, books, fridges,
OL,12,Fdishwashers, cutlery, plates ....
OL,13,Fliterally everything.
OL,15,F"Even our garden at the back,
OL,16,Fobviously we had a lot of equipment in
OL,17,Fthere, which has gone, so ...
OL,18,Fliterally everything had to be
OL,19,Freplaced."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
