PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777389066
OL,3,C'Absolutely amazing': Nursery reopens
OL,4,Cjust six weeks after major fire
OL,6,FOperations Manager Cara Cozens said
OL,7,Fthe speed of the rebuild had been a
OL,8,Fjoint effort, with lots of people
OL,9,Fjoining together to take part.
OL,11,F"It's happened quick, but it's been a
OL,12,Flot of work behind the scenes."
OL,14,FMs Huntley added: "What we've achieved
OL,15,Fis absolutely amazing but you just
OL,16,Fhave to keep going, don't you?
OL,18,F"If you want to reopen. you have to
OL,19,Fkeep going, ut I am quite tired now,
OL,20,Fso I think I do need a bit of a rest."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
