OL,3,C'Absolutely amazing': Nursery reopens
OL,4,Cjust six weeks after major fire
OL,6,FChildren at the nursery are now
OL,7,Flearning in a new modular building,
OL,8,Fwith staff making an effort to keep
OL,9,Feverything, even carpets, as familiar
OL,10,Fas possible.
OL,12,FWork continues to demolish the barn.
OL,14,FThe listed part of the nursery next
OL,15,Fdoor survived and will be refurbished,
OL,16,Fbefore plans go in for the new
OL,17,Fbuilding, with the hope that this will
OL,18,Fbe up and running within 12 to 15
OL,19,Fmonths.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
